Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.99,0:01:03.54,default,,0,0,0,,The 9th game.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.05,0:01:06.65,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,９戦目
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.05,0:01:06.65,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジの賭け距離は１
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.54,0:01:06.01,default,,0,0,0,,The distance Kaiji betted on\Nis 1 mm!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.65,0:01:09.51,default,,0,0,0,,The outcome will\Ndetermine his fate.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.65,0:01:10.12,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,勝つか負けるかで天国と地獄
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.10,0:01:11.94,default,,0,0,0,,Win and survive.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.12,0:01:15.93,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,勝てば生き残り 負ければ破滅
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.12,0:01:15.93,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,破壊する
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.94,0:01:13.66,default,,0,0,0,,Or lose and die!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.12,0:01:15.48,default,,0,0,0,,The destruction is set!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.93,0:01:19.52,default,,0,0,0,,If it extends another 1 mm,\Nthe organ will be destroyed!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.93,0:01:20.26,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,わずか１ミリでも届けば
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.93,0:01:20.26,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,器官を殺す
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.26,0:01:22.24,default,,0,0,0,,It's the game that he can't\Nafford to lose!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.26,0:01:22.56,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,負けられない 一戦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.02,0:01:23.74,kaiji-main-top,,0,0,0,,Limit
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.14,0:01:32.54,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジさん　勝て
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.14,0:01:32.54,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あと１つ 勝つだけだ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.31,0:01:30.40,default,,0,0,0,,Kaiji. You must win!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.40,0:01:32.03,default,,0,0,0,,Just win one more round...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.54,0:01:35.98,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,勝てば無事に出ていける
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.54,0:01:35.98,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,この部屋を
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.55,0:01:35.57,default,,0,0,0,,If you win, then you can\Nleave this room safely.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.98,0:01:38.58,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何も失うことなく
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.01,0:01:38.31,default,,0,0,0,,You won't lose anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.40,0:01:46.55,default,,0,0,0,,The 9th game begins with Kaiji\Non the Emperor side.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.42,0:01:44.32,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,９戦目　１枚目の提出は
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.32,0:01:47.56,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,皇帝側のカイジから
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.55,0:01:49.52,default,,0,0,0,,Of course, he chooses\NCitizen!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.56,0:01:49.76,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,当然 市民
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.98,0:01:56.23,default,,0,0,0,,Open!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.10,0:01:57.94,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,オープン
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.94,0:01:59.94,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,必然の引き分け
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.95,0:01:59.86,default,,0,0,0,,A definite draw.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.94,0:02:02.67,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ここまでは予定調和
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.09,0:02:02.15,default,,0,0,0,,This is just the warm up.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.65,0:02:05.57,default,,0,0,0,,The real game begins from\Nthe 2nd card!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.67,0:02:05.67,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,勝負は２枚目以降
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.02,0:02:10.60,default,,0,0,0,,How should I go about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.05,0:02:14.42,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どう考える？出した後の態度で
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.05,0:02:14.42,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カードを知られてしまう俺は
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.60,0:02:13.71,default,,0,0,0,,He can read my card from my\Nexpression after I put it down.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.38,0:02:17.51,default,,0,0,0,,So I can only use the key card in\Nthe second or fourth round.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.42,0:02:18.59,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,後出しの２枚目か４枚目に
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.42,0:02:18.59,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,勝負するしかない
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.59,0:02:22.59,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どっちで勝負に行くかだが
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.61,0:02:20.68,default,,0,0,0,,Which one should I go for?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.59,0:02:26.96,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,皇帝側はノーリスクで
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.59,0:02:26.96,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,相手の自滅を待てる
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.66,0:02:25.95,default,,0,0,0,,The Emperor waits for the rival's\Nself-destruction without any risk.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.96,0:02:30.60,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だから俺は この２枚目に
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.96,0:02:30.60,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,市民を出しておけば
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.99,0:02:32.46,default,,0,0,0,,So it's safe to use\NCitizen for the second deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.60,0:02:33.00,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,100パーセント 安全な上
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.00,0:02:39.51,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,もし利根川が奴隷を出してきたら
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.00,0:02:39.51,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それであっさり勝ち
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.04,0:02:38.08,default,,0,0,0,,If Tonegawa places a Slave,\Nthen I can win easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.51,0:02:44.25,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,一か八かの賭けは この権利を
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.51,0:02:44.25,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,行使してからでも遅くない
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.52,0:02:43.60,default,,0,0,0,,I can still take a chance\Nafter I get this right.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.25,0:02:46.72,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,勝負は４枚目が賢明
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.28,0:02:46.41,default,,0,0,0,,It's wiser to keep this for\Nthe fourth round.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.72,0:02:49.92,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ならば２枚目は… 市民
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.74,0:02:49.39,default,,0,0,0,,Right, I should put\NCitizen next.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.89,0:02:51.74,default,,0,0,0,,Yes, Citizen!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.92,0:02:52.32,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,けん
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.92,0:02:52.32,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,市民で見！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.29,0:02:58.19,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いや　だからこそ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.29,0:02:58.19,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,皇帝なんじゃないか？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.32,0:02:55.25,default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.86,0:02:58.32,default,,0,0,0,,So maybe I should \Nuse the Emperor then?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.86,0:03:05.37,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺が臆していることを
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.86,0:03:05.37,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,利根川は当然 感じている
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.90,0:03:04.25,default,,0,0,0,,Tonegawa should already\Nknow that I'm afraid.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.34,0:03:06.26,default,,0,0,0,,If that's so,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.37,0:03:12.24,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,となれば 俺が安全策の
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.37,0:03:12.24,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,市民出しに傾くと考えるだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.37,0:03:10.76,default,,0,0,0,,he'd think that I'd play\NCitizen as a precaution.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.24,0:03:15.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,まさか皇帝が来るとは
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.24,0:03:15.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,思わないはず
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.40,0:03:15.27,default,,0,0,0,,He wouldn't know that\NI'd go with an Emperor!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.85,0:03:23.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,理外の理
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.88,0:03:21.77,default,,0,0,0,,The logic beyond logic!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.39,0:03:30.13,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,２枚目　利根川からの提出
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.43,0:03:29.78,default,,0,0,0,,Tonegawa places the 2nd card!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.13,0:03:33.60,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,受けてカイジ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.17,0:03:31.89,default,,0,0,0,,Followed by Kaiji!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.60,0:03:34.52,default,,0,0,0,,Emperor!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.60,0:03:35.60,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,皇帝だ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.60,0:03:40.90,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,行こう　皇帝… 皇帝だ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.78,0:03:39.49,default,,0,0,0,,Go! Emperor!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.93,0:03:41.15,default,,0,0,0,,Emperor!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.84,0:03:48.18,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どうした　行け
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.85,0:03:47.05,default,,0,0,0,,What's the matter? Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.17,0:03:49.93,default,,0,0,0,,Go! Fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.18,0:03:51.98,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,行くんだ 勝負
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.97,0:03:53.18,default,,0,0,0,,Fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.98,0:03:55.72,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,勝負だ　してしまえ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.38,0:03:54.74,default,,0,0,0,,Go...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.65,0:03:56.92,default,,0,0,0,,Fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.72,0:03:57.82,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,勝負！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.59,0:04:05.93,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カード 出そろう　しかし…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.70,0:04:04.41,default,,0,0,0,,The cards are out.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.41,0:04:08.75,default,,0,0,0,,But Kaiji placed a Citizen\Nin the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.93,0:04:08.83,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,結局 カイジが出したのは市民
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.12,0:04:15.02,default,,0,0,0,,Why didn't I play it...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.14,0:04:16.04,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何で出せないんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.04,0:04:19.54,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,皇帝を出せば勝てるのに
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.11,0:04:18.23,default,,0,0,0,,If I played an Emperor,\NI'd have won.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.54,0:04:22.94,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,勝てると分かっているのに
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.54,0:04:22.94,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,なぜ…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.55,0:04:22.50,default,,0,0,0,,I knew I could have won,\Nbut why?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.03,0:04:25.74,default,,0,0,0,,Open!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.05,0:04:27.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,オープン
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.25,0:04:39.68,default,,0,0,0,,What? Which means...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.33,0:04:40.73,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,えっ てことは…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.37,0:04:48.27,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジさん 勝ったよ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.37,0:04:48.27,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,勝った
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.46,0:04:47.79,default,,0,0,0,,Kaiji... won...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.27,0:04:50.21,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,やった　勝った
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.72,0:04:50.39,default,,0,0,0,,All right! Won...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.21,0:04:54.68,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジの気の迷いが幸い
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.39,0:04:52.73,default,,0,0,0,,Kaiji's hesitation was\Nfortunate.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.64,0:04:56.19,default,,0,0,0,,Kaiji won!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.68,0:04:57.45,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジ 勝つ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.45,0:04:59.75,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,生き残りの１勝
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.52,0:04:59.63,default,,0,0,0,,A win that allows him\Nto survive!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.81,0:05:05.97,default,,0,0,0,,Good! Good for you, Kaiji.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.85,0:05:06.32,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,よかった
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.85,0:05:06.32,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,よかったな カイジさん
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.30,0:05:09.48,default,,0,0,0,,You won, Kaiji!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.32,0:05:10.19,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,やった！勝ったよ カイジさん
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.19,0:05:12.19,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,やった
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.23,0:05:11.48,default,,0,0,0,,You did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.80,0:05:20.67,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,気がつけば１人ではなかったのだ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.85,0:05:19.49,default,,0,0,0,,When he became aware of it...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.67,0:05:23.07,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,今 カイジと共に震え
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.71,0:05:22.94,default,,0,0,0,,He realises that he was\Nno longer alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.07,0:05:27.27,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,共にこの生き残りを喜んでくれた
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.07,0:05:27.27,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,仲間がいた
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.08,0:05:27.43,default,,0,0,0,,There were others who shared his\Nfear and joy with him in the game!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.08,0:05:32.00,default,,0,0,0,,Thanks! Thank you,\Neveryone!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.28,0:05:32.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ありがとう　ありがとう みんな
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.76,0:05:36.47,default,,0,0,0,,Why did you lose?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.79,0:05:36.75,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,なぜ負ける？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.75,0:05:40.32,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お前は勝って当たり前だろうが
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.99,0:05:39.97,default,,0,0,0,,You were supposed\Nto win!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.32,0:05:42.26,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,すいません
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.64,0:05:41.88,default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.06,0:05:45.98,default,,0,0,0,,This guy changed his mind at the last\Nmoment when he placed his cards.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.26,0:05:46.13,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,この男 カードを出す瞬間に
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.26,0:05:46.13,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,心変わりしまして
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.13,0:05:48.10,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,勝負がいよいよとなれば
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.23,0:05:51.72,default,,0,0,0,,When push comes to shove, an amateur\Nusually does the opposite.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.10,0:05:50.97,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,安全を追い
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.10,0:05:50.97,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,逆の目に行ってしまうのは
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.97,0:05:57.37,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,素人のお定まりの心理ではないか
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.72,0:05:57.22,default,,0,0,0,,A typical psychological\Nbehaviour!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.44,0:06:03.75,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お前は そんなことも見抜けんのか
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.56,0:06:03.46,default,,0,0,0,,And you can't see through \Nsuch a thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.75,0:06:05.68,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,まるで でくの坊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.83,0:06:08.17,default,,0,0,0,,You're a numskull. A man\Nwho isn't discerning at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.68,0:06:08.55,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,人を見る目のない男だ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.55,0:06:13.19,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,これで その男が安全に逃げれば
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.55,0:06:13.19,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,面白くもない終局
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.60,0:06:13.03,default,,0,0,0,,If this man escapes safely, \Nit will be a dull ending.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.19,0:06:16.09,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,興を失うも甚だしい
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.23,0:06:15.94,default,,0,0,0,,And the mood is totally\Nruined!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.09,0:06:18.19,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,イスだ！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.18,0:06:17.77,default,,0,0,0,,- Give me a chair!\N- Yes, Sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.50,0:06:23.68,default,,0,0,0,,Garbage!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.50,0:06:24.60,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,クズが
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.04,0:06:36.51,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,異様… 異様な叱咤
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.08,0:06:35.76,default,,0,0,0,,That's... A strange rebuke!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.46,0:06:39.76,default,,0,0,0,,I understand the director's\Nwrath at losing his fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.51,0:06:40.02,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,興を失った会長の怒りも
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.51,0:06:40.02,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,分からないじゃない
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.00,0:06:42.00,default,,0,0,0,,But there's no need\Nto be this angry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.02,0:06:42.65,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,が これほど怒ることはない
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.65,0:06:45.24,default,,0,0,0,,There're no guaranteed\Nwins in this game.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.65,0:06:45.92,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,こんなものに
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.65,0:06:45.92,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,必勝法なんてないんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.92,0:06:50.13,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,なのに 利根川は
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.92,0:06:50.13,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ここまで勝ち続けてきた
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.95,0:06:49.24,default,,0,0,0,,But Tonegawa has won\Nevery game so far.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.12,0:06:53.74,default,,0,0,0,,He was more than 90% successful\Nin his predictions until now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.13,0:06:54.43,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,第一 今のだって９割９分
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.13,0:06:54.43,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,看破していたんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.29,0:07:00.48,default,,0,0,0,,And to expect him to read me when\NI put out Citizen in the end...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.43,0:06:58.00,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,最後の最後に 自分でも
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.43,0:06:58.00,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,わけの分からないビビリで
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.00,0:07:00.57,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,市民を出して外すこととなったが
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.48,0:07:03.72,default,,0,0,0,,...because I was afraid\Nis being too strict!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.57,0:07:04.51,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そこまで読めというのは
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.57,0:07:04.51,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あまりに酷
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.51,0:07:08.68,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,会長の怒りは あまりに理不尽だ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.67,0:07:07.58,default,,0,0,0,,The director's wrath is\Ntoo unreasonable.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.68,0:07:12.18,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,異常だ　こんなものミスじゃない
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.71,0:07:12.14,default,,0,0,0,,It's strange. \NThis is no ordinary mistake!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.83,0:07:21.02,default,,0,0,0,,The clue is the director's\N strange rebuke.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.85,0:07:21.76,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,きっかけは
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.85,0:07:21.76,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,会長の異常な叱咤だった
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.76,0:07:24.59,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,その異様な行動に誘発されて
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.87,0:07:24.66,default,,0,0,0,,With that strange behaviour,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.59,0:07:30.90,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジの中で
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.59,0:07:30.90,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ある疑問が急激に膨れあがる
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.66,0:07:29.48,default,,0,0,0,,a question began to form and \Nexpand rapidly in Kaiji's mind
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.82,0:07:31.98,default,,0,0,0,,Illogical...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.90,0:07:34.50,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,不条理… ある理に合わぬこと
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.36,0:07:34.48,default,,0,0,0,,Something isn't going\Naccording to reason!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.48,0:07:41.85,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,負けることはミスじゃない
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.49,0:07:40.49,default,,0,0,0,,His loss wasn't a mistake!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.83,0:07:44.49,default,,0,0,0,,Tonegawa said that\Nhe can read my cards...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.85,0:07:45.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,利根川はさっき
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.85,0:07:45.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺がカードを出す時
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.06,0:07:48.48,default,,0,0,0,,...according to my behaviour\Nwhen or after I place them!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.08,0:07:48.72,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あるいは出した後の態度で
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.08,0:07:48.72,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何を出したか分かる
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.72,0:07:49.90,default,,0,0,0,,That's what he said!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.72,0:07:51.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そう言った
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.12,0:07:54.52,default,,0,0,0,,But why did he say that \Nin the middle of the game?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.15,0:07:55.99,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,なぜ この戦いの最中に
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.15,0:07:55.99,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,言ったんだ？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.99,0:07:58.99,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それは利根川にとって
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.99,0:07:58.99,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,不利益しか生まないはずだ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.02,0:07:59.17,default,,0,0,0,,That will only put Tonegawa\Nat a disadvantage.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.90,0:08:03.07,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あの発言があったからこそ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.09,0:08:03.06,default,,0,0,0,,It's only after he said\Nthose words...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.06,0:08:06.36,default,,0,0,0,,...that I decided to use my key\Ncard when I play after him.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.07,0:08:06.27,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺は勝負を
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.07,0:08:06.27,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,後出しの時にしようと決めた
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.77,0:08:10.74,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あの発言がなければ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.79,0:08:10.47,default,,0,0,0,,If I didn't know that,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.74,0:08:15.01,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺は先出しの時に
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.74,0:08:15.01,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,勝負に行ったかもしれない
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.87,0:08:13.80,default,,0,0,0,,I'd have gone for it \Neven when playing first.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.96,0:08:16.02,default,,0,0,0,,If so,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.01,0:08:16.95,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そうなれば
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.95,0:08:20.85,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺の態度でカードを知り得る
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.95,0:08:20.85,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,利根川に負けはない
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.00,0:08:20.12,default,,0,0,0,,then Tonegawa will never lose\Nsince he can read my expression.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.85,0:08:23.72,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,必勝だ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.98,0:08:22.30,default,,0,0,0,,A sure win!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.72,0:08:30.49,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,なのに ヤツはあの不用意な発言で
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.72,0:08:30.49,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,その目を完全に消した
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.80,0:08:28.83,default,,0,0,0,,But with that unexpected statement, \Nthat chance is gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.49,0:08:34.80,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,この一事がどう考えても変
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.58,0:08:33.54,default,,0,0,0,,No matter how you look at it, \Nthat statement is strange!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.79,0:08:40.05,default,,0,0,0,,The director didn't care about that\Nthough he was angry with the loss.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.80,0:08:37.57,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,負けたことに
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.80,0:08:37.57,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あれほど激怒した会長が
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.57,0:08:40.80,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,この本当のミスは まるで無視
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.76,0:08:42.48,default,,0,0,0,,He didn't even bring it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.80,0:08:45.61,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,話題にすら上げない
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.80,0:08:45.61,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,これもおかしい
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.71,0:08:44.11,default,,0,0,0,,That is strange too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.61,0:08:49.91,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,３つの違和感
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.61,0:08:49.91,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,利根川の不用意な発言と
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.62,0:08:47.29,default,,0,0,0,,The three strange occurrences.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.59,0:08:49.56,default,,0,0,0,,Tonegawa's slip of the tongue.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.91,0:08:52.82,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それを無視する会長
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.94,0:08:51.83,default,,0,0,0,,The director who ignored that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.82,0:08:56.09,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そして会長の異様な怒り
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.92,0:08:55.53,default,,0,0,0,,And his strange wrath!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.03,0:08:58.53,default,,0,0,0,,The thought that\Nthese lead to...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.09,0:08:58.69,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,これらが導き出すものは…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.92,0:09:04.56,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,隠蔽？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.08,0:09:02.26,default,,0,0,0,,A concealment?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.56,0:09:05.78,default,,0,0,0,,A concealment?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.56,0:09:07.83,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,隠蔽か？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.80,0:09:12.11,default,,0,0,0,,That statement is a trap that \Nconceals something else.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.83,0:09:12.54,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あの発言は
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.83,0:09:12.54,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,別の重要な何かを隠すオトリ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.53,0:09:13.85,default,,0,0,0,,In other words, it's a decoy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.54,0:09:17.37,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いわばダミー　陽動作戦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.77,0:09:17.12,default,,0,0,0,,A diversion tactic!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.37,0:09:22.35,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,つまり ヤツはこちらの動作で
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.37,0:09:22.35,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カードを察していたわけじゃなく
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.45,0:09:22.06,default,,0,0,0,,This means that they're not reading\Nmy cards from my behaviour.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.35,0:09:27.05,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,もっと別の何かで
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.35,0:09:27.05,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,知っていたんじゃないか？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.50,0:09:25.85,default,,0,0,0,,They know it through\Nanother way!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.05,0:09:30.72,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そして会長のあの怒りから
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.05,0:09:30.72,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,察するに
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.08,0:09:30.74,default,,0,0,0,,And judging from how angry\Nthe director was,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.72,0:09:35.82,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,その何かは 勝って当たり前
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.72,0:09:35.82,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,というような絶対的なもの
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.74,0:09:36.07,default,,0,0,0,,that something is a sure-win method\Nthat will guarantee victory!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.40,0:09:40.68,default,,0,0,0,,A setup?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.43,0:09:41.73,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,イカサマ…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.14,0:09:54.64,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ひょっとしてこいつら
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.14,0:09:54.64,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,イカサマを？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.18,0:09:54.67,default,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me these guys\Nset me up?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.28,0:10:00.61,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,こいつら… こいつら！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.32,0:10:00.39,default,,0,0,0,,These scoundrels...\NThese scoundrels...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.61,0:10:04.55,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジ様　次の賭け距離は？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.64,0:10:01.73,default,,0,0,0,,Mr Kaiji.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.58,0:10:04.15,default,,0,0,0,,What's your next bet?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.55,0:10:06.95,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,１
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.74,0:10:05.68,default,,0,0,0,,1 mm.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.68,0:10:06.63,default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.02,0:10:12.83,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,しかし どうやって？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.13,0:10:12.27,default,,0,0,0,,But how?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.83,0:10:18.37,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,後ろからは のぞかれていない
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.83,0:10:18.37,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,上か？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.86,0:10:14.82,default,,0,0,0,,Am I being spied on\Nfrom behind...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.61,0:10:16.14,default,,0,0,0,,Above?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.37,0:10:20.97,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いや カメラらしきものもない
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.42,0:10:21.24,default,,0,0,0,,No... There doesn't seem\Nto be a camera around.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.51,0:10:28.18,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ガンカードでもなかった
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.58,0:10:26.34,default,,0,0,0,,Neither are these\Ntrick cards.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.18,0:10:33.11,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,一体 どうやって… どうやって？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.22,0:10:30.02,default,,0,0,0,,So how...?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.54,0:10:31.76,default,,0,0,0,,How?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.11,0:10:38.92,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,10戦目　１枚目の提出は
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.11,0:10:38.92,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,皇帝側の利根川から
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.30,0:10:38.36,default,,0,0,0,,The 10th game begins with\NTonegawa on the Emperor side.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.92,0:10:41.12,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,続けてカイジ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.12,0:10:40.76,default,,0,0,0,,Next comes Kaiji.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.66,0:10:47.49,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,オープン　当然の引き分け
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.74,0:10:44.86,default,,0,0,0,,Open.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.38,0:10:46.77,default,,0,0,0,,A draw of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.46,0:10:49.28,default,,0,0,0,,The problem is the 2nd card.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.49,0:10:49.43,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,問題は２枚目
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.43,0:10:53.30,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジが先出しの２枚目
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.58,0:10:52.04,default,,0,0,0,,The card Kaiji has to\Nplace first!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.30,0:10:55.24,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ガンカードでないなら
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.35,0:10:55.02,default,,0,0,0,,If they aren't trick cards,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.02,0:10:57.87,default,,0,0,0,,someone must be telling him\Nwhat my cards are.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.24,0:10:59.24,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺のカードを知らせている
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.24,0:10:59.24,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,協力者がいるはずだ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.24,0:11:02.01,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,しかし
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.42,0:11:00.28,default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.01,0:11:07.35,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,パッと見る限り 俺のカードを
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.01,0:11:07.35,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,のぞいている人間はいない
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.22,0:11:06.10,default,,0,0,0,,At a glance, there's no one\Nwho can peek at my cards...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.35,0:11:09.55,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,確認しうる人間はいないんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.40,0:11:09.70,default,,0,0,0,,No one who can\Nsee them...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.72,0:11:13.79,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いや いる
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.77,0:11:13.03,default,,0,0,0,,No, there is.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.79,0:11:15.92,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,１人いる
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.42,0:11:15.71,default,,0,0,0,,There is one.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.92,0:11:20.76,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,このフロアで俺のカードを
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.92,0:11:20.76,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,見ている人間が１人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.98,0:11:19.77,default,,0,0,0,,One person on this floor \Nwho can see my cards.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.76,0:11:23.66,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それは 俺だ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.84,0:11:23.00,default,,0,0,0,,And that is... Me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.66,0:11:28.04,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ひょっとして俺自身が
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.66,0:11:28.04,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,サインを送っているのか？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.79,0:11:27.00,default,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me I'm the one \Nwho's been signaling to them?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.04,0:11:30.94,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,態度とかそぶりとか
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.04,0:11:30.94,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そんな あいまいなことじゃなく
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.07,0:11:31.10,default,,0,0,0,,Not intangible things like\Nbehaviour or body language,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.94,0:11:34.27,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,もっと明白な何かを送っていて
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.10,0:11:33.92,default,,0,0,0,,but something much clearer...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.27,0:11:37.64,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それを利根川が受け取っている？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.38,0:11:36.70,default,,0,0,0,,And Tonegawa's receiving that?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.64,0:11:41.74,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,えっ？利根川の目線が
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.64,0:11:41.74,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カードを見ていない
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.80,0:11:42.16,default,,0,0,0,,What? He's not looking\Nat his cards.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.78,0:11:45.82,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,もっと下
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.88,0:11:47.63,default,,0,0,0,,He's focusing on something\Nbelow. His watch!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.82,0:11:48.76,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,むしろ時計
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.76,0:11:50.89,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,時計？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.92,0:11:50.26,default,,0,0,0,,Watch?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.87,0:11:53.75,default,,0,0,0,,No way! There should\Nstill be time left!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.89,0:11:53.79,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,バカな　まだ時間はあるはずだ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.80,0:11:59.63,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,確かにその点は問題ない
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.97,0:11:58.11,default,,0,0,0,,You're right about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.63,0:12:04.54,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,逆… あの時と今
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.63,0:12:04.54,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,時計のはめ方が逆
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.72,0:12:00.84,default,,0,0,0,,It's different!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.25,0:12:04.14,default,,0,0,0,,He's wearing his watch\Nin a different way now!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.54,0:12:06.67,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,なぜ…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.68,0:12:09.15,default,,0,0,0,,Why? It must be to win!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.67,0:12:09.88,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,決まってる　勝つためだ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.88,0:12:14.68,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,利根川は ああすることによって
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.88,0:12:14.68,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何か決定的な情報を得ていた
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.90,0:12:14.23,default,,0,0,0,,By doing that, Tonegawa's getting\Nsome crucial information...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.68,0:12:20.42,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,つまり俺が何のカードを
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.68,0:12:20.42,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,出したかを…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.77,0:12:18.76,default,,0,0,0,,Something to do with what\Ncards I'm playing!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.42,0:12:26.09,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あの時計は受信機
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.42,0:12:26.09,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺の心の動揺を受信する機械
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.43,0:12:22.22,default,,0,0,0,,That watch is a receiver.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.53,0:12:25.40,default,,0,0,0,,A machine to receive the \Nvibrations of my heart!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.09,0:12:29.43,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,てことは送信機もある
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.14,0:12:29.25,default,,0,0,0,,Which means...\Nthere's a transmitter too!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.43,0:12:32.83,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何を出したか感知し
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.43,0:12:32.83,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,送信する機械が
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.48,0:12:32.97,default,,0,0,0,,It senses what cards I play\Nand transmit the data to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.57,0:12:42.84,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,これだ　これが感知器！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.65,0:12:40.82,default,,0,0,0,,This is it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.01,0:12:44.38,default,,0,0,0,,This is a sensor\Nand a transmitter!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.84,0:12:45.35,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そして 送信機
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.35,0:12:48.38,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,この装置は俺の脈拍や血圧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.41,0:12:48.58,default,,0,0,0,,This instrument senses\Nthe changes in my pulse,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.38,0:12:52.12,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,体温の変化を感知して
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.38,0:12:52.12,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,送ってるんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.58,0:12:53.57,default,,0,0,0,,blood pressure and body temperature,\Nand sends it to that watch!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.12,0:12:54.12,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あの時計に
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.12,0:12:58.79,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,10戦目
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.29,0:12:57.71,default,,0,0,0,,The 10th game.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.79,0:13:01.26,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,２人のカードが出そろい
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.91,0:13:00.87,default,,0,0,0,,Both their cards are out.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.26,0:13:04.63,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,オープン
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.39,0:13:02.60,default,,0,0,0,,Open!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.63,0:13:07.63,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,当然のごとく 利根川の勝ち
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.65,0:13:07.34,default,,0,0,0,,It is of course\NTonegawa's win.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.63,0:13:10.47,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジのカードはまたも見破られ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.84,0:13:10.34,default,,0,0,0,,Kaiji's cards are being\Nread once more.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.47,0:13:13.07,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,これで利根川の７勝３敗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.63,0:13:13.58,default,,0,0,0,,Tonegawa has won 7\Nand lost 3 games!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.99,0:13:29.22,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そうだ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.20,0:13:28.59,default,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.22,0:13:32.96,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,考えてみれば しょっぱなの選択
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.25,0:13:32.10,default,,0,0,0,,Thinking about it,\Nthe option at the start...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.96,0:13:36.50,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,目か耳かという選択からしてそう
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.04,0:13:36.10,default,,0,0,0,,I was given the option of\Nmy eye or my ear!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.50,0:13:39.60,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,この選ばせるという行為が
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.50,0:13:39.60,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,疑いを消す
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.55,0:13:40.05,default,,0,0,0,,I won't suspect anything if\NI were given the option.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.64,0:13:45.44,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,演出する 偽りの公正感を
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.66,0:13:42.95,default,,0,0,0,,An act!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.54,0:13:45.68,default,,0,0,0,,An act of fairness!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.11,0:13:51.01,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あの時計も巧妙
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.20,0:13:50.25,default,,0,0,0,,That watch is also an\Ningenious plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.01,0:13:53.91,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,５分間と時間を制限することで
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.18,0:13:54.05,default,,0,0,0,,With a time limit of\N5 minutes,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.91,0:13:57.58,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,時計を見るという行為の
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.91,0:13:57.58,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,不自然さを消す
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.05,0:13:57.12,default,,0,0,0,,he won't be suspected if\Nhe keeps looking at the watch!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.58,0:14:01.82,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,この２つの道具の疑わしささえ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.58,0:14:01.82,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,払拭できれば
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.67,0:14:01.12,default,,0,0,0,,With these 2 instruments\Nnot suspected at all,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.82,0:14:05.03,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あとは利根川の舌先三寸の弁舌で
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.90,0:14:04.83,default,,0,0,0,,he just has to conceal the strange\Ncoincidence of a sure win...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.03,0:14:07.96,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,後出しの時に必ず勝つ不自然さを
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.11,0:14:10.10,default,,0,0,0,,...every time he plays after me...\Nwith his smooth talk!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.96,0:14:10.76,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カモフラージュすればいい
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.76,0:14:16.04,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そう考えると 勝負を12戦までと
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.76,0:14:16.04,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,定めたのもうまい
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.84,0:14:15.25,default,,0,0,0,,The setting for 12 games\Nis also ingenious!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.04,0:14:17.97,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,これくらいなら
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.04,0:14:17.97,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,気づかれることなく
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.11,0:14:19.21,default,,0,0,0,,That's the ideal number of rounds\Nthat will prevent...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.97,0:14:22.68,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だましおおせる…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.97,0:14:22.68,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そんな絶妙な回数
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.67,0:14:21.71,default,,0,0,0,,...the opponent from\Nfinding out about the setup!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.68,0:14:27.41,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,汚い　汚い　汚い
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.71,0:14:26.07,default,,0,0,0,,Dirty! Dirty! Dirty!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.40,0:14:29.25,default,,0,0,0,,An unforgivable act!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.41,0:14:30.18,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,許し難い行為
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.18,0:14:33.59,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,しかし だからといってどうする？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.27,0:14:33.12,default,,0,0,0,,But even if it's so,\Nwhat can I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.59,0:14:36.02,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,このイカサマを
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.59,0:14:36.02,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,言い立てたところで
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.72,0:14:38.80,default,,0,0,0,,Even if I expose them, they'd have\Nsomething to back them up!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.02,0:14:39.59,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,当然 ヤツらは
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.02,0:14:39.59,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,知らぬ存ぜぬで通す
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.59,0:14:41.83,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あの時計を見せろと言っても
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.63,0:14:41.33,default,,0,0,0,,If I ask to see the watch,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.83,0:14:46.30,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どこかのスイッチを押せば
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.83,0:14:46.30,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,受信機としての機能が解除
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.94,0:14:45.46,default,,0,0,0,,there might be a switch somewhere\Nto stop its receiver function.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.30,0:14:50.17,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,一瞬で普通の時計に戻ることも
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.30,0:14:50.17,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ありうる
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.36,0:14:49.36,default,,0,0,0,,It would then become\Na normal watch once again.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.17,0:14:53.37,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,暴いても無駄　どうにもならない
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.36,0:14:53.70,default,,0,0,0,,It's useless to make a fuss.\NThere's nothing I can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.51,0:14:58.41,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,その時 ひらめく
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.57,0:14:58.55,default,,0,0,0,,At that moment...\NA flash of inspiration!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.41,0:15:01.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,圧倒的ひらめき
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.55,0:15:00.31,default,,0,0,0,,A tremendous spark\Nof genius!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.15,0:15:05.75,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジ様　次の賭け距離は？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.15,0:15:05.75,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジ様
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.18,0:15:03.71,default,,0,0,0,,Mr Kaiji. How much\Nwill you bet next?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.54,0:15:05.69,default,,0,0,0,,Mr Kaiji.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.75,0:15:08.12,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,黒服の声すら届かない
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.88,0:15:08.06,default,,0,0,0,,Even the voice of that guy\Ncan't reach him.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.12,0:15:11.99,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それほどの閃光が
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.12,0:15:11.99,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジの脳を刺す
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.24,0:15:12.93,default,,0,0,0,,That wonderful idea pierced Kaiji's\Nbrain like a bolt of lightning!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.99,0:15:14.29,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ひらめく
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.67,0:15:21.95,default,,0,0,0,,A wicked move to\Nkill the devil!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.73,0:15:23.87,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,悪魔を殺す悪魔的奇手
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.73,0:15:23.87,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,利根川殺し
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.95,0:15:23.30,default,,0,0,0,,A move to kill Tonegawa!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.87,0:15:27.81,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジ様　あの…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.96,0:15:25.87,default,,0,0,0,,Mr Kaiji... hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.81,0:15:31.28,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どこまで設定してある？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.04,0:15:29.54,default,,0,0,0,,How far does it extend?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.73,0:15:30.53,default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.28,0:15:35.48,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,この耳の装置 針はどこまで
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.28,0:15:35.48,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,伸びるように設定してある？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.34,0:15:32.89,default,,0,0,0,,This ear piece.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.15,0:15:35.71,default,,0,0,0,,How deep does\Nthe needle go?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.02,0:15:41.09,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,45ミリまでだ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.24,0:15:40.79,default,,0,0,0,,Until 45 mm.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.09,0:15:45.79,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,てことは
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.09,0:15:45.79,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,今 27ミリ費やしてるから
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.27,0:15:45.29,default,,0,0,0,,So that means since the needle\Nhas already moved 27 mm,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.79,0:15:49.96,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あと18ミリは針を伸ばすことが
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.79,0:15:49.96,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,可能ってことだよな
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.94,0:15:49.49,default,,0,0,0,,it can still extend\Nanother 18 mm.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.96,0:15:53.97,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そうだが
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.96,0:15:53.97,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,じゃあ この18ミリ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.10,0:15:51.53,default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.81,0:15:56.54,default,,0,0,0,,Then it's possible to bet\Nthe rest of the 18 mm?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.97,0:15:56.60,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,すべてを賭けること 可能か？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.12,0:16:16.96,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,自分が今 何を言っているのか
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.12,0:16:16.96,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,分かってるのか？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.40,0:16:16.50,default,,0,0,0,,Do you know what\Nyou're saying?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.96,0:16:18.96,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,血迷いおって
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.18,0:16:18.52,default,,0,0,0,,You're mad.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.96,0:16:22.30,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,言っとくが 30ミリなら
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.27,0:16:20.29,default,,0,0,0,,I'm telling you this.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.32,0:16:26.30,default,,0,0,0,,At 30 mm, only the ear drum is hurt\Nand you lose nothing else.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.30,0:16:26.70,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,負けても鼓膜までで
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.30,0:16:26.70,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それ以上 失うことはない
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.70,0:16:29.47,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いや それすらいっときのこと
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.83,0:16:29.22,default,,0,0,0,,And even that is temporary.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.47,0:16:32.44,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,鼓膜は破れてもたやすく再生する
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.61,0:16:32.30,default,,0,0,0,,Even if you hurt your eardrum,\Nit will heal easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.44,0:16:35.71,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,しかし 鼓膜の先 中耳を越え
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.67,0:16:38.31,default,,0,0,0,,But once you pass the ear drum to\Nthe middle and the inner ear,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.73,0:16:38.31,kaiji-Sign-top,,0,0,0,,[Eardrum, middle ear, inner ear]
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.71,0:16:37.94,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,内耳の領域を
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.71,0:16:37.94,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,破壊していくとなると
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.94,0:16:39.88,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そうはいかん
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.31,0:16:39.62,default,,0,0,0,,it becomes complicated.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.83,0:16:42.19,default,,0,0,0,,The inner ear is complex\Nand fragile.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.88,0:16:43.52,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,内耳は複雑かつデリケートだ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.74,0:16:43.31,kaiji-Sign-top,,0,0,0,,[Semi circular canal, cochlea]
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.52,0:16:48.36,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,再生は不可能というより
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.52,0:16:48.36,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,最悪の場合 死
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.62,0:16:45.07,default,,0,0,0,,It cannot heal.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.48,0:16:50.02,default,,0,0,0,,In the worst case,\Ndeath is a real possibility!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.36,0:16:51.86,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,これも覚悟すべきだ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.86,0:16:54.66,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,仮に助かったとしても…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.86,0:16:54.66,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,利根川
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.02,0:16:53.60,default,,0,0,0,,Even if you're saved...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.60,0:16:54.90,default,,0,0,0,,Tonegawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.32,0:16:59.20,default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that good?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.33,0:17:01.87,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,よいではないか　いや それ以上だ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.58,0:17:01.30,default,,0,0,0,,No, that's even better.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.87,0:17:07.67,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジ君が勝負してくれれば
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.87,0:17:07.67,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,こんなに喜ばしいことはない
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.91,0:17:06.52,default,,0,0,0,,With Kaiji investing so much,\Nnothing's more delightful than this.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.67,0:17:09.98,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ぜひ 受け入れるべき
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.73,0:17:10.03,default,,0,0,0,,We should take him on!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.98,0:17:12.61,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,45ミリのリミットいっぱい
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.03,0:17:12.69,default,,0,0,0,,The maximum limit\Nis 45 mm.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.61,0:17:17.21,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,18ミリの張りを慈悲の心でな
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.69,0:17:17.05,default,,0,0,0,,Take his bet of 18 mm\Nwith benevolence!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.22,0:17:22.06,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジ君は負ければ破滅
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.33,0:17:21.78,default,,0,0,0,,If you lose, you will die.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.06,0:17:27.03,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,しかし なに
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.06,0:17:27.03,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,勝てばいいんだよ 勝てば
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.22,0:17:26.79,default,,0,0,0,,But so what? You just\Nhave to win. Just win.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.79,0:17:31.85,kaiji-Sign-top,,0,0,0,,[Emperor, Slave]
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.03,0:17:31.06,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジ君は奴隷サイドだから
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.03,0:17:31.06,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,５倍の収入
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.26,0:17:30.97,default,,0,0,0,,If you win, you'll benefit from\Nthe payout rate of a Slave.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.06,0:17:34.50,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,18かける５で900万だ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.16,0:17:34.30,default,,0,0,0,,And that is 18 times 5...\N9 million!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.50,0:17:39.07,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ということは このあと
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.50,0:17:39.07,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジ君が２連勝すれば
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.59,0:17:39.16,default,,0,0,0,,This means if you win\Ntwo straight games,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.07,0:17:42.04,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,900かける２で1800万
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.16,0:17:42.04,default,,0,0,0,,9 times 2...\NYou'll get 18 million!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.04,0:17:45.88,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,すでにカイジ君が得ている
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.04,0:17:45.88,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,210万と合わせると
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.30,0:17:46.04,default,,0,0,0,,And with the 2.1 million\Nthat you've already won,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.88,0:17:51.38,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,最初に目標にしていた2000万に
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.88,0:17:51.38,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,届くではないか
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.04,0:17:50.05,default,,0,0,0,,you can finally reach\Nyour goal of 20 million.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.20,0:17:55.01,default,,0,0,0,,What a coincidence!\NHow great!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.38,0:17:55.86,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何という偶然だ　喜ばしい
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.82,0:17:58.79,default,,0,0,0,,If so, there's no need\Nto hesitate.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.86,0:17:58.83,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,なら もう迷うこともない
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.83,0:18:01.33,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,おい 18だ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.05,0:18:00.60,default,,0,0,0,,Hey, 18 mm then!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.60,0:18:01.41,default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.33,0:18:03.43,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,待て！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.41,0:18:02.44,default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.14,0:18:12.34,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,少し考えさせてくれ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.41,0:18:12.27,default,,0,0,0,,Let me think about this\Nfor a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.85,0:18:27.95,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジさん
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.92,0:18:27.55,default,,0,0,0,,Kaiji...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.79,0:18:37.35,default,,0,0,0,,I can win for sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.83,0:18:39.13,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あの手で勝てる　勝てる
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.55,0:18:39.89,default,,0,0,0,,I can win. I can win!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.13,0:18:41.80,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,勝てる
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.80,0:18:44.57,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,問題は
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.84,0:18:43.06,default,,0,0,0,,The problem is...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.57,0:18:48.97,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,勝つための最終ハードル
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.57,0:18:48.97,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あれができるかどうか
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.62,0:18:46.47,default,,0,0,0,,This is the last battle...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.22,0:18:48.88,default,,0,0,0,,It's whether I can\Npull it off or not...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.22,0:19:01.86,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いや できるかどうかじゃない
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.37,0:19:01.18,default,,0,0,0,,No. It's not a matter of\Nwhether I can do it or not!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.86,0:19:03.79,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,やるんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.91,0:19:03.08,default,,0,0,0,,I have to!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.79,0:19:08.89,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,このＥｶｰﾄﾞで俺が初めてつかんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.79,0:19:08.89,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,勝機らしい勝機じゃないか
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.03,0:19:08.70,default,,0,0,0,,This is my first and only chance\Nat winning in E-Card!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.30,0:19:14.60,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,やらなくてどうする？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.38,0:19:14.22,default,,0,0,0,,Why am I not going for it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.04,0:19:20.84,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,勝つために生きなくて どうする
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.07,0:19:20.60,default,,0,0,0,,If I want to live,\NI must win!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.29,0:19:42.26,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,誰だ？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.31,0:19:40.49,default,,0,0,0,,Who is it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.26,0:19:44.93,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あの…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.26,0:19:44.93,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何だ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.48,0:19:44.49,default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.93,0:19:47.83,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,その… 張りませんよね？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.02,0:19:45.97,default,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.20,0:19:47.73,default,,0,0,0,,You wouldn't do it, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.83,0:19:51.40,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そんな命を張るようなマネしちゃ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.83,0:19:51.40,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ダメですよ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.99,0:19:51.23,default,,0,0,0,,Doing something like that to \Nput your life on the line.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.40,0:19:53.41,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,生きてなんぼじゃないですか
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.47,0:19:53.49,default,,0,0,0,,There's always a way\Nif you live.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.41,0:19:56.31,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,これは俺だけじゃなくて
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.41,0:19:56.31,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,みんなも…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.66,0:19:56.64,default,,0,0,0,,This is not just my view,\Nbut everyone else's too.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.31,0:20:01.11,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,みんな カイジさんに
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.31,0:20:01.11,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,助かってほしくて
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.61,0:20:01.33,default,,0,0,0,,Everyone wants Kaiji\Nto be saved.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.11,0:20:05.45,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,１人じゃない
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.11,0:20:05.45,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジさんは１人じゃ…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.33,0:20:04.01,default,,0,0,0,,You're not alone. \NYou're not alone, Kaiji.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.12,0:20:11.16,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そうだ　俺の計画は１人じゃダメ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.19,0:20:12.36,default,,0,0,0,,That's right. My plan can't\Nproceed with just one person.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.16,0:20:14.29,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,助けが… 協力者が必要
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.55,0:20:14.25,default,,0,0,0,,I need an ally!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.29,0:20:17.60,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カ… カイジさん？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.01,0:20:16.05,default,,0,0,0,,Kaiji...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.60,0:20:20.30,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お前が協力しろ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.70,0:20:19.21,default,,0,0,0,,You shall assist me!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.30,0:20:22.64,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,これは天の声なんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.40,0:20:22.26,default,,0,0,0,,This is the command\Nof heaven!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.64,0:20:27.34,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,11戦 12戦と勝てば
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.64,0:20:27.34,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,2000万に到達するという符号も
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.67,0:20:26.88,default,,0,0,0,,The sign that I'll get 20 million,\Nwinning the 11th and 12th game...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.34,0:20:30.24,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お前が今 ここに来たことも
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.39,0:20:29.64,default,,0,0,0,,And that you're here now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.24,0:20:34.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,天が俺に勝てという合図… 啓示
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.40,0:20:33.42,default,,0,0,0,,All these are the signs\Nthat I'll win.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.15,0:20:36.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,死んだ石田さんや佐原が
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.33,0:20:35.87,default,,0,0,0,,An omen!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.87,0:20:40.81,default,,0,0,0,,Ishida and Sahara are telling me to\Navenge them and defeat Tonegawa!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.15,0:20:38.28,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺に かたきを取れ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.28,0:20:41.19,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,利根川を倒せと言ってるんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.19,0:20:45.19,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,やる　やるんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.19,0:20:45.19,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺は勝たなければならない
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.36,0:20:43.01,default,,0,0,0,,I'll do it! I'll do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.26,0:20:45.07,default,,0,0,0,,I must win this!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.19,0:20:47.49,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お… 落ち着いてください
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.50,0:20:47.29,default,,0,0,0,,Please calm down!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.49,0:20:52.63,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,勝つって言ったって
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.49,0:20:52.63,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,奴隷側は圧倒的に不利なんですよ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.58,0:20:51.32,default,,0,0,0,,Even if you say so, you're at a\Ndisadvantage on the Slave side!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.63,0:20:55.54,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,道はある
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.65,0:20:53.82,default,,0,0,0,,There is a way!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.04,0:20:54.92,default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.54,0:20:57.64,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,まず…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.55,0:20:56.83,default,,0,0,0,,Firstly...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.37,0:21:01.16,default,,0,0,0,,Like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.37,0:21:02.67,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,こうだ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.94,0:21:08.44,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジの奇怪な行動の
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.94,0:21:08.44,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,意味するものは…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.00,0:21:08.57,default,,0,0,0,,What are Kaiji's strange\Nactions all about?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.72,0:21:15.32,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そして利根川殺しの
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.72,0:21:15.32,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,悪魔的奇手とは
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.81,0:21:15.08,default,,0,0,0,,And what is the wicked plan\Nto kill Tonegawa?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.32,0:21:19.82,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジ　すべてを賭けて今 挑む
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.41,0:21:19.78,default,,0,0,0,,Kaiji's putting everything on\Nthe line to meet the challenge!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.33,0:22:45.46,default,,0,0,0,,Next, Fierce god.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.38,0:22:45.68,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,次回｢鬼神｣
